# Network Intrusion Detection System (NIDS)

A network-based intrusion detection system project built, capable of detecting suspicious activities and generating alerts. This project includes custom rule creation, alert logging, and real-time visualization using tools.

---

## Project Overview

- **Tool Used**: Snort / Suricata (choose one)
- **Monitoring Interface**: `eth0` (or your interface)
- **Visualization**: Kibana / Grafana
- **Log Format**: EVE JSON / Syslog
- **Simulated Attacks**: Nmap, Hping3, Metasploit

---

## Tools & Technologies

| Component        | Technology Used         |
|------------------|-------------------------|
| IDS Engine       | Snort / Suricata        |
| Log Format       | JSON / Syslog           |
| Dashboard        | Kibana / Grafana        |
| OS Platform      | Ubuntu / Kali Linux     |
| Packet Sniffing  | Wireshark / Tcpdump     |

